<li><a href="https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/alloc/boxed/struct.Box.html#impl-IntoIterator-for-Box%3C%5BI%5D,+A%3E"><code>impl IntoIterator for Box&lt;[T]&gt;</code></a></li>
