<li><a href="https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/alloc/boxed/struct.Box.html#impl-FromIterator%3Cchar%3E-for-Box%3Cstr%3E"><code>impl FromIterator&lt;char&gt; for Box&lt;str&gt;</code></a></li>
