<h3><a href="#other-changes" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="other-changes"></a>Other changes</h3>
<p>Check out everything that changed in <a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/releases/tag/1.80.0">Rust</a>, <a href="https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/cargo/CHANGELOG.html#cargo-180-2024-07-25">Cargo</a>, and <a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rust-clippy/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#rust-180">Clippy</a>.</p>
